HEADWORD: Molybdous
<hw>Mo*lyb"dous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Molybdena</er>.]</ety> <def>Of, pertaining to, or containing,
molybdenum; specif., designating those compounds in which molybdenum has
a lower valence as contrasted with <contr>molybdic</contr>
compounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mome</ent>⟦br⟧
